<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">9的倍数法，方法一，乘数是9的倍数，即相邻的两数和是9，如18、27、63...等，或是中间数是9、99、999...；首尾之和是9，如297,5994，7992...，可以利用它的尾补数凑整，转化为同数，运用跟踪乘。为了充分利用跟踪乘，有些异数可并拆为同数。可将被乘数与凑整后的乘数相乘，再减去被乘数与乘数凑整的位补数相乘的积，所得的数就是要求的积。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">26×63=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 26×63</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=26×(70-7)</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=26×70-26×7</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=1820-182</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=1638</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>